{"tid":2431451,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"又有垃圾港豬喺黃竹坑唔戴口罩畀市民影相！！","createTime":"2021-03-03T15:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T15:56:33.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7456a8abf6fe3ca61dc307b1a88f66f94caad43d","tid":2431451,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T15:53:18.000Z","msg":"2021-03-03 20:55<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/none/573a302c3fbb3a50580f7c646410fcae/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210303/_2021030321004262023.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2F573a302c3fbb3a50580f7c646410fcae%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210303%2F_2021030321004262023.jpg&h=76b1cf86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n野豬自由自在闖蕩港鐵站。網民Ken Tso圖片<br />\n<br />\n港島不時有野豬出沒，有市民昨日目睹一隻野豬闖入黃竹坑港鐵站。<br />\n<br />\nfacebook群組「50+友 精彩人生」有網民昨日早上，目睹一隻野豬大搖大擺悠閑地經行人天橋進入港鐵站大堂，沿途市民好奇觀望，但野豬自得其樂。<br />\n<br />\n發相網民留言說，「深灣很多野豬，經常有一百幾十隻攔路等嘢吃」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民說，「我昨天見到一隻豬媽五隻豬存在深灣道公園搵食」、「早幾日清晨時份見到隻大豬公在南濤閣和雅濤閣之間山邊搵食，相信是一家人」、「佢梗係好耐冇食嘢隻豬都咁瘦唔係肥豬」。有網民戲謔「唔知呀豬哥有無帶八達通呢」<br />\n<br />\n圖片轉載自facebook群組「50+友 精彩人生」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/432p0/0x0/100/none/4ae9a45623125860a149b045eafa5ae0/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210303/_2021030321004651530.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F432p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2F4ae9a45623125860a149b045eafa5ae0%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210303%2F_2021030321004651530.jpg&h=c9dcf17c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n野豬自由自在闖蕩港鐵站。網民Ken Tso圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/432p0/0x0/100/none/7da16d91e427a962515efacbcb608dab/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210303/_2021030321021048944.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F432p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2F7da16d91e427a962515efacbcb608dab%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210303%2F_2021030321021048944.jpg&h=54080bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網民指香港仔不時有野豬出沒。網民Ken Tso圖片"},{"pid":"83f599d5e79283f048cc50a95465421f781b336e","tid":2431451,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T15:56:33.000Z","msg":"一隻gmail<br />\n二隻gmail<br />\n三隻gmail<br />\n..."}]}